From a631b9ea8af83162b958fce7501a183284ef0e14 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ashanti Nichole Montano <montano.214520@globalcity.sti.edu.ph>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 04:26:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Replace About section photo and update per-villa pax
 capacities

- AboutSection: replaced /images/misc/about.jpg with the new poolside
  photo provided, layout and all surrounding code left unchanged.
- Updated guest capacity to be villa-specific instead of a uniform
  30-50 range: Villa 1 up to 34, Villa 2 up to 40, Villa 3 up to 50,
  Villa 4 up to 40, Villa 5 up to 34 pax.
- Applied this consistently across VillaShowcase (cards + modal +
  summary badge), Footer villa list, HowToBook guest capacity stat,
  LiveChat chatbot answers, TermsModal capacity list, FAQSection
  capacity list, and BookingCTA (villa pax field + all 3 places that
  displayed pax in the booking form, now driven by that field instead
  of a hardcoded string).
---
 public/images/misc/about.jpg         | Bin 295219 -> 123046 bytes
 src/app/components/BookingCTA.tsx    |  18 +++++++++---------
 src/app/components/FAQSection.tsx    |  10 +++++-----
 src/app/components/Footer.tsx        |  10 +++++-----
 src/app/components/HowToBook.tsx     |   2 +-
 src/app/components/LiveChat.tsx      |   4 ++--
 src/app/components/TermsModal.tsx    |  12 ++++++------
 src/app/components/VillaShowcase.tsx |  22 +++++++++++-----------
 8 files changed, 39 insertions(+), 39 deletions(-)

